HEADWORD: mahl-stick
<hw>mahl"-stick`</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G. <ets>malerstock</ets>; <ets>maler</ets> a painter
+ <ets>stock</ets> stick.]</ety> <def>A long stick that a painter uses
to support the hand holding the brush while painting. Same as
<er>Maul-stick</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
